getCost(int[][], int, int, int) - Static method in class mesquite.align.lib.AlignUtil
Given a matrix, int[][] subs, containing costs for going from state i to state j, and two int a and b representing 32-bit state sets, and the alphabetLength, this method calculates the minimum cost for going between the two statesets.
